    The Fib4 number sequence is a sequen ce si milar to the Fibbonacci sequnece that's defined as follows:
    fib4(0)-> 0    fib 4 (1) ->0
    fib 4(2) -> 2
   fib4(3) -> 0
  fib4(n) -> fib 4(n-1) + fib4 (n-2) + fib4(n-3)+ fib4(n -4).
    Please write a functi on to effic ientlycompute t hen-th element of the fib4number sequence.  Do no t use recursion.
